    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an uncompromising 2008 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.1) in showroom condition. This specimen is powered by the 3.8L M97.01 naturally aspirated flat-six, delivering 355 horsepower through a 6-speed manual transaxle with shortened shift throws. The mechanical integrity is superlative, featuring Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The cooling system has been pressure-tested, and the bore-scoring inspection is clear, ensuring the internal tolerances remain within factory parameters. Every bushing, link, and damper performs with the rigidity of a new vehicle. Finished with concours-level paint depth and a pristine undercarriage, this 911 represents a rare opportunity for the purist seeking an analog driving experience in a flawlessly preserved chassis.",
