      "description": "This is, without hyperbole, a true showroom-quality specimen. From the moment you lay eyes on the deep, mirror-like finish of the original factory paint\u2014protected by a professional-grade multi-layer ceramic coating\u2014you\u2019ll understand why this vehicle stands apart. There are zero rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks on the bodywork. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium hand-stitched leather seats show absolutely no bolster wear, and the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since day one. Every button, switch, and digital interface functions with the crisp tactile feedback of a brand-new vehicle. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has been exclusively serviced at the authorized dealership, and I have a comprehensive binder of every service record to prove its meticulous upkeep. It has spent its entire life in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen rain or snow. The undercarriage is as clean as the roof, free from any road debris or oxidation. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or a discerning driver to own a vehicle that has been maintained with an obsessive level of care. All original keys, window sticker, and a clean title are ready for the next owner.",
